{"tid":2338952,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺得呢個世界無好老闆？","createTime":"2020-12-24T10:14:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-25T03:55:17.000Z","uid":382363,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"edd47662dc37fda88311d174d95fa2cde3e0ead0","tid":2338952,"uid":382363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T10:14:22.000Z","msg":"我唔要求好老闆 但正常都無<br />\n大部分老闆請你番黎預左你一黎直接做<br />\n唔好要我教 我無咁多時間比你<br />\n好似係一種工具咁<br />\n最好請一個一入黎就自動波<br />\n如果唔達上司期望 下屬又要受氣<br />\n上司好直接 不用理你有乜感受<br />\n因為人工包左<br />\n最慘係人工又唔係高 <br />\n上司既一半人工都無<br />\n但佢地永遠就預左你可以幫佢搞掂好 唔洗煩佢<br />\n我都明上司請個人番黎係希望咁<br />\n達唔到期望1到2個月就直接炒你<br />\n唔洗同你客氣<br />\n<br />\n大公司比較多衰老闆<br />\n有無ching分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f862cc56adf62913c092a2ece13bbfbe2a45f03d","tid":2338952,"uid":61831,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T10:15:25.000Z","msg":"你可以創業做好老闆"},{"pid":"20d46d14d8e66e7da3737179e1f20680b6ce6fe9","tid":2338952,"uid":325863,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T10:17:46.000Z","msg":"當老闆要理每一個員工感受，老闆可以收檔啦"},{"pid":"f7d95aa0ac44368e969ccb758e5cfcdb148f4cb1","tid":2338952,"uid":382363,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"20d46d14d8e66e7da3737179e1f20680b6ce6fe9","tid":2338952,"uid":325863,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T10:17:46.000Z","msg":"當老闆要理每一個員工感受，老闆可以收檔啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T10:18:19.000Z","msg":"我個老闆得我一個下屬"},{"pid":"a999f5406cbc466652206cce20e85643566662be","tid":2338952,"uid":353493,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T10:37:50.000Z","msg":"想你自動波都叫有機會呀<br />\n有啲人連自動波既機會都無仲要俾老屎忽跣<br />\n仲要俾埋信封話唔幫手 直接要人走 <br />\n真係唔明咩運作"},{"pid":"00d13a4993d190960f5cf7d36a66c97177a223b3","tid":2338952,"uid":104965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T10:40:57.000Z","msg":"慘得過有D老闆係能力好低<br />\n同佢解釋自己做嘅野佢又唔明<br />\n又會因為佢能力低而拖曬全隊人後腳"},{"pid":"05875053de8af518e33d681cd66fff83472fb596","tid":2338952,"uid":242921,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T10:44:52.000Z","msg":"當然無好老板，但亦無好員工。<br />\n<br />\n打和啦。"},{"pid":"ec03837bc65693e7704ea3941232fe34d24d84a7","tid":2338952,"uid":37719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T10:47:39.000Z","msg":"好老闆執9晒"},{"pid":"59ac841a96200adf911dcecd0cebf4a3893afe49","tid":2338952,"uid":342891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T12:41:02.000Z","msg":"員工有價值老闆自然好"},{"pid":"049a9504c066a37b3a3f56a330abbd96e1c41741","tid":2338952,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T14:07:08.000Z","msg":"當你做老闆又唔同諗法<br />\n點解員工唔同你博命<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0126240116580cdd46099b734762aa5840836f8f","tid":2338952,"uid":356506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T14:34:46.000Z","msg":"有 我老細"},{"pid":"5eea56d9f3887b70cb7e0fcb3be59719f69736ae","tid":2338952,"uid":376679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T18:37:19.000Z","msg":"絕對明白你感受 <br />\n呢個世界上冇好老闆 ， 因為老闆都係自私嘅。"},{"pid":"738afd617160e7f3515dc7a0810340d8ba7a1bff","tid":2338952,"uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T19:12:03.000Z","msg":"正常<br />\n<br />\n請你返嚟梗係直接做, 做得好係應份<br />\n<br />\n點解腦細要出錢請你返嚟, 而你又做唔到, 仲要慢慢教？<br />\n<br />\n要學嘢, 你返學校, 你比錢阿SIR教你<br />\n<br />\n返工唔係腦細比錢你學嘢<br />\n<br />\n明唔明乜嘢叫「返工」？<br />\n<br />\n分到「返工」同「返學」未？"},{"pid":"c6b265a7c3108ce5e1a59c593826543b78696d53","tid":2338952,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5eea56d9f3887b70cb7e0fcb3be59719f69736ae","tid":2338952,"uid":376679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T18:37:19.000Z","msg":"絕對明白你感受 <br />\n呢個世界上冇好老闆 ， 因為老闆都係自私嘅。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T19:13:53.000Z","msg":"腦細係做生意, 係呢個高度競爭既商業社會求存<br />\n<br />\n唔係善堂<br />\n<br />\n你要唔自私既, 去社署"},{"pid":"b03fe80c04882368e721e3e5ef68dbb55ac03493","tid":2338952,"uid":68624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T19:19:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c568beaeb3e130e992df532b619c93257778241","tid":2338952,"uid":248299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T19:20:38.000Z","msg":"打過幾份工拍過幾個老細都幾好<br />\n閪既得一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca8414aed117a4514ca8af3a7dc24f8e1b7e2bc8","tid":2338952,"uid":194298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T19:29:15.000Z","msg":"上司會有好人，老闆一定無個好人 (係管理下屬方面)"},{"pid":"87f5d1dd8b8c49a2d20bb0bcdb73b5e7e0cca8b7","tid":2338952,"uid":145769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T19:42:32.000Z","msg":"我遇到好多好老細或者上司<br />\n覺得自己比較好彩<br />\n<br />\n唯一一次遇過係辭咗職<br />\n打返嚟話你唔見咩喎要你賠<br />\n明屈你要你賠錢<br />\n跟住又拖你佣<br />\n打官司咁濟<br />\n有錢架喎，不過個人仆街"},{"pid":"be3d3dbbffde739c8d96beb7b0efc70554cd292d","tid":2338952,"uid":342691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T19:49:09.000Z","msg":"老闆嘅存在就係剝削員工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68aff4806e1f1c5ccbc9314323be7409420af2e7","tid":2338952,"uid":246571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T19:49:35.000Z","msg":"做得老闆都係為錢姐🙂"},{"pid":"ecfb08d8403abff7a26047c7d8e61024f00874d5","tid":2338952,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"be3d3dbbffde739c8d96beb7b0efc70554cd292d","tid":2338952,"uid":342691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T19:49:09.000Z","msg":"老闆嘅存在就係剝削員工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T20:06:55.000Z","msg":"咁員工返工咪一樣會吞POP"},{"pid":"64103c839f500d26e4da927ed4df609d3f286187","tid":2338952,"uid":15954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote